#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:3
msgid "Automatic partitioning failed"
msgstr "自動磁碟分割失敗了"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:3
msgid ""
"This probably happened because there are too many (primary) partitions in "
"the partition table."
msgstr "這或許是因為在磁碟分割表中有過多的 (主) 磁碟分割區。"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:10
#. New,2004/03/01
msgid "Choose what to automatically partition:"
msgstr "選擇要在哪裡進行自動磁碟分割"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:10
#. New,2004/03/01
msgid ""
"If you select a whole drive, the automatic partitioning will remove or "
"resize existing partitions on the selected drive, which can cause data loss."
msgstr "如果您選取了整個裝置，自動磁碟分割會在所選取的裝置上進行分割區的移除、"
"或是變更現有分割區的大小，因而可能會導致資料的遺失。"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:18
msgid "Partitioning scheme:"
msgstr "磁碟分割方案："

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:18
#. Fuzzy
msgid ""
"Several different partitioning schemes are available. If you are unsure, "
"choose the first one."
msgstr "有好些不同的方案可以用來進行分割磁碟。如果您不確定，請選擇第一個。"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:24
msgid "Unusable free space"
msgstr "無法使用的未使用空間"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:24
msgid ""
"Automatic partitioning failed because the chosen free space may not be "
"used.  There are probably too many (primary) partitions in the partition "
"table."
msgstr ""
"自動磁碟分割失敗的原因似乎是因為所選擇的未使用空間無法使用。在磁碟分割表中可"
"能有過多的 (主) 磁碟分割區。"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../templates:37
#. Fuzzy
msgid "Automatically partition a drive"
msgstr "對裝置進行自動磁碟分割"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:41
msgid "Use the largest continuous free space"
msgstr "採用最大的連續未使用空間"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. for example "Use entire drive: IDE0 master - Maxtor 46L489"
#: ../templates:46
#. New,2004/03/01
msgid "Use entire drive: ${DEVICE}"
msgstr "使用整個裝置：${DEVICE}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:50
msgid "Partition with custom settings"
msgstr "採用自訂的設定來進行磁碟分割"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:54
#. Fuzzy
msgid "Automatically partition the free space"
msgstr "對未使用空間進行自動磁碟分割"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:58
msgid "/, /home and swap"
msgstr "/、/home 及 置換空間"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:62
msgid "/, /usr, /usr/local, /var, /var/mail, /tmp, /home and swap"
msgstr "/、/usr、/usr/local、/var、/var/mail、/tmp、/home 及 置換空間"

#~ msgid "Use ${DEVICE} entirely"
#~ msgstr "使用整顆 ${DEVICE}"

